Welcome to Grootspoor.com

As a specialist in G / IIm scale we are, as no other, aware of what a G-scale railways enthusiast wants. We will be glad to be of service.

We sell new and used items from different manufacturers.

LGB, Toytrain, Playmobil, USA trains, Aristocraft, Bachmann, Kiss, etc.

From rolling stock up to track and scenery.

We barter and buy single pieces and (very large) collections and can offer you a good price. Discretion and quick service is guaranteed.Mailing service

Are you searching for a specific model? We are glad to keep you informed about our stock of used items. Please inform us of you specific wish or request and we will contact you personally as soon as it is in stock. Please apply for our mailing service. We will keep you informed about our changes in used stock, special offers and interesting news. Apply now!
